faceoff_negative.comments:
Pros: pigmentation of the product is great for neutral to warm skin tones;
Long lasting

Cons: formula dries quickly. Once placed on the skin, start blending asap. There's a 60 second window before the blend-ability of the product ends; blending within the 60 second window can even be a challenge if, you're not using the right tool (use a damp blending sponge), and/or using too much product (a little goes a long way
